// mockApi.js
import axios from 'axios';
import MockAdapter from 'axios-mock-adapter';

// Create a mock instance
const mock = new MockAdapter(axios, { delayResponse: 500 });

// Mock a GET request to fetch the list of items
mock.onGet('/api/muddamaal').reply(200, [
  {
    id: 1,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.S.-68/15',
    crimeDate: '27-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '32/15',
    category: 'other',
    quantity: 2,
    value: '₹ 00',
    status: 'P.O. Stay. at',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:17',
    details: '1. A bamboo stick 2. A captured washer',
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.E.-44/15',
    crimeDate: '27-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '31/15',
    category: 'other',
    quantity: 2,
    value: '₹ 00',
    status: 'P.O. Stay. at',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:17',
    details: '1. A bamboo stick 2. An iron poly pipe',
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.S.-64/15',
    crimeDate: '25-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '30/15',
    category: 'vehicle (in commission of crime)',
    quantity: 1,
    value: '₹ 25000',
    status: 'has been returned',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:14',
    details: 'One white color access car GJ-18-Shirikaya-4678',
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.S.-29/15',
    crimeDate: '24-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '29/15',
    category: 'other',
    quantity: 2,
    value: '₹ 2',
    status: 'P.O. Stay. at',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:14',
    details: '1. A torn book written for a cricket betting deal 2. A ballpoint pen',
  },
  {
    id: 5,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.S.-29/15',
    crimeDate: '24-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '29/15',
    category: 'Currency',
    quantity: 2,
    value: '₹ 400',
    status: 'P.O. Stay. at',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:14',
    details: 'Three notes of 10 2. Three notes of 100, 1 note of 50 and 2 notes of 10',
  },
  {
    id: 6,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.S.-29/15',
    crimeDate: '24-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '29/15',
    category: 'Mobile and Electronic Equipment',
    quantity: 8,
    value: '₹ 55500',
    status: 'has been returned',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:14',
    details: `1. A phone of Samsung 2. A phone of Intel 3. A phone of Intelco 
              4. A phone of Intel 5. A phone of Nokia 6. A phone of Nokia 
              7. A phone of Nokia 8. A TV of Panasonic company`,
  },
  {
    id: 7,
    crimeNo: 'Gu.2.No.E.-231/14',
    crimeDate: '22-02-2015',
    muddamaalNo: '28/15',
    category: 'vehicle (in commission of crime)',
    quantity: 1,
    value: '₹ 20000',
    status: 'has been returned',
    custodyLog: 'Custody Log',
    custodyDate: '03/02/2024 13:07',
    details: 'A Mo. Cycle GJ-18-AD-6162',
  }
]);

// Mock a POST request to add a new item
mock.onPost('/api/muddamaal').reply(config => {
  const newRecord = JSON.parse(config.data);
  return [200, newRecord];
});

export default axios;
